I"5<h2 id="graphql-ide">GraphQL IDE</h2>

<p>Although not strictly necessary, youâ€™ll likely want a GraphQL IDE to easily form and test GraphQL queries.  Here are a few examples of GraphQL IDEs you can use:</p>

<ol>
  <li><a href="https://insomnia.rest/graphql/">Insomnia</a></li>
