<p>Once you install a GraphQL IDE, you should now be set to fire your first GraphQL query!</p>

<p>As an example, you can try a very basic query like the following, with your QuickBooks company and OAuth 2.0 bearer token retrieved in the previous section.</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>query getCompanyName {
  company {
    companyName
    companyType
  }
}
</code></pre></div></div>
